  <brief_title>Chromogranin-A-Derived Peptides and Periodontitis in Diabetic Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Chromogranin-A-Derived Peptides in the Gingival Crevicular Fluid and the Saliva of Diabetic Patients With or Without Periodontitis</official_title>
